Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是桔梗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了粥过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗你以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再照顾我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到那边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到姐姐偷偷救了一个\N叫鬼蜘蛛的强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能跟犬夜叉说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依那家伙的个性\N他一定会吃醋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  助我一臂之力好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然没头没脑的这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人\N来拜托我去消灭妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也有点招架不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的报酬可是很高的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  往你那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  那是它的本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你姐姐手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个叫做\N四魂之玉的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道四魂之玉的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那些坏蛋\N全都盯着那个四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那个玉\N越是沾染上仇恨的鲜血就会变得越邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姐姐会把四魂之玉净化\N不会让它变邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗总是装得一本正经\N圣洁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人真想看看\N那个女人慌乱时候的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到这一点\N我就越来越兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛说了那样的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  老实说我好讨厌他喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕这辈子\N都只能躺在那里不能动弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初桔梗姐姐是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从姐姐的这种仁慈之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么感觉到了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在樱花树下\N站得太久的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的气息就会变得不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为这樱花的缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你\N跟我上次见到的时候完全变了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的灵力怎么变得这么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只怕那些妖怪\N还有魑魅魍魉之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会突破你设下的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说\N是你释放出这些妖怪咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然真的被男人迷了心窍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方就是那个\N无法完全进化的半妖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把四魂之玉交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我代替你\N来净化那颗四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕你没有这个本事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想取你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的邪恶想法\N把我们招引过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我听听看\N你的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一个\N能够自由活动的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能让四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和桔梗完完全全的属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过交换条件是\N必须把你的灵魂交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到\N我这个腐朽的灵魂还有点用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对地\N给我身体还有力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进步了很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来对付那些\N特别难缠难以战胜的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被射中的妖怪会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将永远沉睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要唤醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有当射箭的人发自内心\N希望这个妖怪苏醒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才可以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要特别小心这棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这棵神木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这棵树叫做时代树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说拥有穿越时空的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时代树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被封印在这棵树上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个妖怪的肉体就不会腐烂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这么多的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真大意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没有注意到\N这么强大的邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  妖怪们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  把四魂之玉抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉将会赐予你们\N这个世界上最强大的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们将会成为最强大的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把巫女桔梗杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来得太晚了  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的灵力真的变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血刃飞爪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼的眼睛怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子  是我害了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切全都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我这个姐姐太不争气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要那么自责了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟人家打架本来就常常\N会有这种意外发生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有战斗的话\N你就不再是你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前你也问过这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想放弃战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想放弃战斗\N然后试着当平凡的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本就有一半的血液\N是人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉如果落到\N邪恶的妖怪手中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的妖力就会越来越增强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你利用它的力量\N来变成人类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那颗玉就会得到净化\N就可能会就此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是四魂之玉的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉如果不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将变成一个普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  我愿意变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有丝毫的迟疑犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N你也要成为一个普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了\N不用再多说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知道  还问这种傻问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天中午
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西边森林的神木前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带着四魂之玉过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能让你称心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太期待  没耐心等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能现在就把我变成人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要无理取闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道夜晚\N四处充满了邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用四魂之玉的话\N得等太阳升起来之后才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N天亮之后要马上进行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还很早  你继续睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  你不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐只是去\N帮你采些药草回来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药草这里不是已经有很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想也许还有更有效的药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐再去找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫  你的眼睛还会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  今天好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么\N那时候的我觉得特别空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里很希望姐姐能留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她今天不要去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我强烈地这么祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉这家伙\N是不是睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你用这个来化妆\N你的本性也不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这口红根本就不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该用妖怪的血\N来妆点妆点就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从头到尾从来没有半点\N想成为人类的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉\N我就不客气的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗玉还得吸收\N更多仇恨的鲜血才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把村里的人都杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一开始\N就打算欺骗我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句话也是谎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有丝毫的迟疑犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到那个半妖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出现啦  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你半妖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那双难看的狗耳朵\N难道听不见我说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能\N把四魂之玉交给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在这里一决生死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉\N就会因为憎恶和仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而受到污染
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  你是骗我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想利用我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来\N我以后就不再叫你半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这样说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么现在又…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了这个\N我就可以成为真正的妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就再也不会有人\N敢叫我半妖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉费我这么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉费我是这么信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来都没有\N怀疑过你的用心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你却… 可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤的好重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你怎么会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我就这样死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要再多说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算最后变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听好  小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这颗四魂之玉\N跟我的尸体一起烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要让它\N再落入邪恶之徒的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把它\N一起带到那个世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后过了五十年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N一直被封印在神木上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N还是那个时候的老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就已经知道自己的生命\N到了尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此\N为什么没有射出破魔之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是射出了封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在这一棵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说能超越时间的\N时代树神木上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把犬夜叉封印起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N仇恨姐姐失去四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且被封印在\N神木上的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又流露出\N如此安详平静的面容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来我还是想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N是不是能够有明白的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的第一个孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可爱的女孩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不哭  不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字叫戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你朋友打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预习的笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我今天会带去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
